Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 收音机嘎吱嘎吱 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 尖叫声 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 风扇呼呼旋转 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!（￣ε(#￣)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西\N飞起来挺棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊，我觉得\N如果操纵着大一些的飞行器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以造成一些\N有效伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至可能把一个人干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等等……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 仔细想了想 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们开始节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--{\c&H00FFFF&} Captions by vitac{\c} --\N{\c&HFFFF00&} www.Vitac.Com{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,captions paid for by\NDiscovery Communications
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[ whirring ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜这个故事是关于\N无人机的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，但实际上这一集中我们有\N两个棒棒哒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,关于飞行器的流言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个是关于\N这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是首先我们\N要讲一个精彩的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,蛟龙夫人对你来说意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想谈这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哦尅，我们可能想到不同的方面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因为蛟龙夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是灯塔国空军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在50年代对传奇般的高空侦察机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,U-2的昵称
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 收音机嘎吱嘎吱 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧，流言是关于什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 收音机嘎吱嘎吱 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，流言表示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,U-2侦察机是所有飞机中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,最难操纵起降的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} [ 广播中传来{\i}\N{\i1} 坚定的声音 ]{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该近距离看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,美国空军是绝对不会\N让我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,接近这么个玩意儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对讲机： C1, 34.8, 34.8.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我一开始也是这么想的\N但是奇迹般的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们允许了\N你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亲自\N参观他们的U-2项目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看这些\N飞机操作是有多难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N那我们还等什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么可等的了\N让我们干♂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 模仿飞机引擎咆哮 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Man:\N它笔♂直得升起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像喷气推进的四柱架子床
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\N航空的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,被逆向空气动力学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,挑剔的飞行员和糟糕的设计再次推动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这在世时间最长的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,价值最高的\N美国空军飞行工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也是最难操纵的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为开展这个调查\N我们该去只有那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Radio chatter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Plane engine roaring ]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经得到那些\N有关U-2的疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将在这里得到一一解答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在正站在U-2项目的研发地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是这些飞机被提供服♂务的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是飞行员训练的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在飞到全球各个角落去执行他们的任务之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须能够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里找出流言的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们甚至要登上飞机飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 为了开始弄懂要完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这个奇迹般的航空器有多难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当，杰米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是声名狼藉却又庄严的U-2蛟龙夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: \N有着比任何空军飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都久的U-2飞行经历的巴塞洛缪少校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,将按照规范训练亚当和杰米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,最初设计始于50年代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bartholomew: 单发引擎,\N高空飞行, 超长翼展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,超强推力, 超大抬升力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以携带很重的荷载到一个很高的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后续航很久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这架飞行器带给飞行员的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,众多且意义重大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是所有的燃料都装在机翼中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，飞机在起飞时并不能支持住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他重量巨大的机翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bartholomew:\N当机翼即将提升
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,机翼下方的辅助轮将脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie: 然后侦察任务将是漫长的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,并且将在一个非常高的高度执行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这需要复杂的增压服科技
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,和极端情况下的安全保障功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的东西都是这么薄这么轻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,却又十分坚固
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,最关键的是降落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它的降落十分猛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,以为只有一个主要的起落架承载所有的重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Man: 6, 5, 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie: 轮子沿着机身的中心线分布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以它看起来就像降落一辆自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当机身倾向一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这些制动垫料将会保护翼梢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie: 我们之后将看到\N即使是接近之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行员也无法看到跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Man: 3...2...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们通过另一名驾驶员驾驶追逐车辆来解决这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Man: Two hold at 1 inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,目前来看，流言的情况不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\N这是个令人影响深刻的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对飞行员有着挑战的核对表\N但是接下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须亲自看一看这个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为了那个目的，杰米和我已经\N被放行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,去搭一趟\N到宇宙边缘的顺风车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我们将着手于为期一个礼拜的训练项目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的我们将用一礼拜的时间学习如何成为一名乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是, 只有一人份的空间供我们中的一个人进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Air hissing ]\NWOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 蛤蛤蛤 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了x3让我进♂去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以下一个故事是致命无人机？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是，就是，确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If the press\Nis to be believed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,无人机将在未来运送我们的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至是我们的披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有些人认为它们是 致命的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,潜在的 一目了然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,无人机可能将在一阵狂风中袭击你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然后螺旋桨将……咻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,切断你的喉咙杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这听起来像\N他是为我们定制的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是我所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们去测试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 但是用什么测试这个流言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,首先\N亚当和杰米全方位的浏览了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,无人机技术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,从巨大的尺寸开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie:\N让我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的定制摄像平台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,它有八个电动机和2800W的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它携带着自稳定高解析3磅重相机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Loud voice ] 超酷，不是吗?\N[ Loud whirring ]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 然后在模型的另一边...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是基础消费级别的四轴飞行器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他麻雀虽小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,却五脏俱全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,螺旋桨，电机……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie: [ 蛤蛤蛤 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,任何科技都有它的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 但是作为流言的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,人类将会成为它的受害者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,无人机真的可能致命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为认真开始他们的探索\N需要回到工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这里，亚当有两个中规模的模型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,最可能用于商业快递
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,左边的这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,即时飞出盒子的小模型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大一点的是中级的模型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有着一切你想要飞行的部件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要组装起他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这一个已经准备好飞行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我将试一试这实际上有多容易飞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, aah, aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,非常容易飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当前造成的损伤是非常启蒙性的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, aah, aah!\N观念的证据是很需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,恶，他滴下妹汁在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 为了搞明白一个普通螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也能造成一条新鲜的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当和杰米将一条标准尺寸的叶片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,装在棍子上以飞行时的速度旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一只鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的教训是肯定是不解自明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,随时待命，Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Blade whirring ]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,液~要来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,液~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看就在那里，我的朋友，那里有一个伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们来面对一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不仅仅在讨论伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在讨论毁灭性的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着我们确实在讨论这条静脉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这条颈静脉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得如果我们继续试验
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要制作一个脖子当做试验平台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能够伸进我们的螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\N接下来，在流言终结者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能给我搞一条邦迪®创可贴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\N亚当正将脖子伸向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,致命无人机的血腥故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跳伞！跳伞！跳伞！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: ...大家正在准备有生之年的飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam: 又复杂又吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 无人机运输会致命吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: Adam and Jamie已经准备好了证明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,液~来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\N现在，切深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我们要证明其中一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可以切进另外一个，我们需要各一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是很容易在商店买到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这些就不是那么容易搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要自己制作一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为了做到这个，我要用很多很多的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,和这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他被切断，将喷出血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这将会很精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\N液噗，亚当制造
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a mortal mannequin that will\Nreact accurately to an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我将要做的基本要点就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是铸造一个脖子\N用弹道明胶.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这脖子多高，这些人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有管子在里面所以我可以灌入蓝色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为了视觉体验
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这需要很靠近表皮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我将有效地铸造这些静脉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,运用这些黄铜棒材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像想内想外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 随着模具和血管的就位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候来制作假肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,杰米和我发现，这东西和子弹发生的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很像人体和子弹所发生的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但为了得到皮肤和肌肉的韧性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要把这个玻璃纤维填料添加到弹道凝胶里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们在铸造模具时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, 真漂亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh，到目前为止，我对这一切表示很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不基于任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 设置好了以后，就是一段短暂的缓解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,新鲜的喉咙从模具中取出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就要出♂来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Bleep ] [ Bleep ]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Bleep ]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Groaning ]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好了就是这样，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 然后亚当将蓝色的血加入到系统中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: .然后测试他那在解剖学上完全正确的静脉模型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在皮下正确的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} That{\i} is a bleeding neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,以及需要正确大小的力来切割
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，谁能给我个邦迪创可贴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,让我给你介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,已经介绍的很顺口了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这基本上就是个用来流血的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,当是致死的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这套系统现在有不止两条静脉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我们喉咙只有两条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们就可以测试好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要通过旋转脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,液，就像是多功能的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想测试几次就测试几次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还能看蓝色的血液喷出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝色的血液从静脉喷出，我要闭嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 但是在亚当的蓝血假人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被放置在无人机的杀伤范围之下前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们回到比尔空军基地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来测试u-2是否是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最难驾驶的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 引擎轰鸣 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到高海拔生理学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和增压服操作指南
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当和杰米都在为了在飞机上测试流言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而刻苦训练
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人会上天，一个人会留下待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样打开你的头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从几个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很简洁的简介开始……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,泥萌会用到一个像这样的增压服控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,关于安全装备……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个备份增压系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,以及紧急程序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会教你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如何安全地伞降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是几分钟长的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,空姐的安全示范
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,首先它可以用来防止减压病的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: And a clear indication\Nof the enormity of the endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的机舱失压，增压服会膨胀起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你失去了直觉，内部的充气……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这段时间内你的面罩会被冰覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不到……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果你不得不割断绳索来脱离……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我们现在还无法亲身飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们已经学会了所有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,必须知道的解决方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息是你有一个紧急弹射座椅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,坏消息是，你必须
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拉动自己座位上的紧急弹射手柄来离开飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是嘘嘘这样的事情，呃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也像是困难重重的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,向下拉，往旁边锁死，然后你就可以开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小心♂翼翼地嘘嘘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我……我不觉得……我不想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在不知道它们作用的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对着一堆按钮按来按去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这需要一点小小的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这些复杂的设备有什么卵用？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么u-2计划是除了NASA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“你特么的在逗我”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,和太空计划之外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一使用增压服的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,穿增压服的主要目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,防止缺氧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，其中之一，当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为u-2的飞行高度远高于其他任何飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,进入了超过50000英尺（约合15240米）高的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的“空间等效区域”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但更重要的是当{\i1}我们{\i}到达那个高度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们{\i}会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的进化程度让我们可以在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,从海平面到10000英尺（约合3048米）高处之间正常呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,8减3是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,8减3等于4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们处于这个高度之上时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就难以正常吸入氧气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,打开开关，不然你会死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,打开开关！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 无线电干扰声 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因此，增压服和机舱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,必须人为地增加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,空气压力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,来保证飞行员的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一项可以解决这个问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,意义重大的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要拉下红色的系索……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它可能会打到你的脸……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它会在你的增压服内侧放出一个钩子……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在整整一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,紧张的学习之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,第三天来临了 我们的菜鸟新兵……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,训练时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了体能训练
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想看看最酷的东西吗？hhh看这个！徽章！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在撞击课程中——当飞机坠毁时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,应该如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是军队上三个星期的空降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和伞降训练
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你全部的训练内容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是极好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚经历了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果必须在高空弹射出飞机时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所有可能出现的紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,酷毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,伞降时会发生什么，如何着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样着陆十分容易
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,会坏掉……有些地方会摔伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,最特别的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤蛤蛤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚学会了 当我的降落伞被树挂住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我被吊在半空时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,该如何放低自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 娇♂喘 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈，来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让降低我的高度自己安全地落到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,降低我的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[ bluuuuuuuuuu ]\N灰常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望所有这些技巧只需要在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这间安全的房子里用到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:真是漫长而疲劳的一天.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,弹出 弹出 弹出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 这场测试的绝对规模，科技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和在太空边缘飞行所需的专业姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是显而易见的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,两个词蹦到我的脑子里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,错综复杂，胆战心惊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:三天的信息过载之后……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所使用的紧急弹射装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,也在哥伦比亚号航天飞机的前四次飞行中使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:并且驾驶蛟龙夫人的困难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也显现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但它真的是最难驾驶的飞机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为了搞清这个问题，流言终结者们已经准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在太空边缘飞行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,它们就像我的太空睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:尽管士气高涨……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 妹子的笑 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 先生 你能听到我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}能 我现在感觉想要跳舞{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:...开始增压了，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，拿来……[ 做英文字幕的就没听清= = ]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:杰米和亚当还需通过最后一个训练阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以准备飞行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}哦♂~{\i}\N你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}非一般的感觉{\i}\N蛤蛤蛤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} 事实上 感觉并不怎么样{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 嘶~ ]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} 嗷w{\i}\N我会降低压力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see somebody\Nfeeling like panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是……有很多东西要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: 他们每人都要在增压服内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,进行一次全系统的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来就是高空紧急情况模拟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在杰米被塞进了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,高空气压模拟室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,左右手套都连接好并且锁死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It will replicate\Nthe lack of pressures
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that he might experience\Nunder different circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in that very suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: The environment\Ninside the chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,will simulate\Nthe flight plan of a u-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Jamie,\Nwhat we're gonna do now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is bring the chamber up\Nto 5,000 feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,check the ears and sinuses and\Nmake sure they're clearing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: If the cabin pressure\Nof the u-2 was to fail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How you feelin' right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I feel fine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:...Jamie needs to prove\Nhe can operate the suit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and emergency systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So right now we're just doing\Na slow ascent up to, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,flight level 4-0-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: As they approach\Ncruising altitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a startling reminder\Nof the dangers involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: A breaker of water\Nat body temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If Jamie's suit were to fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what the liquids\Nin his body would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go ahead\Nand try to reach that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ejection handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\NWith that thought in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and at maximum altitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie has a few tasks\Nto complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Down by\Nyour right buttocks there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the scramble handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it up towards your chin\Njust a little bit. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: The final being\Nthe suits automated response
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to a sudden cabin pressure\Nfailure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,3...2...1...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And go ahead and pull\Nthat helmet hold down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Clicking sound ]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, uh, it's kind of scary,\Nactually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of force,\Nand when they, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,decompressed rapidly,\Nit's just like, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sort of feeling like\Npopcorn. [ Chuckles ]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: While Jamie clearly\Ndidn't enjoy the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he did pass muster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Chuckles ] Oh, awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\NCue fanboy savage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Singsongy ] Oh, the gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The coolest thing about this is,\NI'm not just wearing a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even wearing a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man. That's far out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Air hisses ]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing the apex\Nof decades of tens of thousands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of people problem solving how to\Nsurvive in hostile conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can feel that technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! [ Laughs ]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel how reliable\Nthey've made things
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to touch and understand\Nwith your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this borne\Nby hard experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people gave their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so that this suit\Ncould protect these pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you good to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, everything about this\Nkind of astounds me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that people do this\Nevery single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting climber 5,000 feet\Nat 5,000 feet coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam:\NIt takes a team of people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to put me\Nin this suit correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your comfort level?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm farting up a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But more than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,once I was under the simulated\Ndepressurization...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there we go. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...where the suit would inflate,\Nit gets incredibly tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Locate the ejection handle\Nin between your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you go, sir,\Nyour fingers around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there we go. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam: These guys have to be\Nin incredible shape
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was just sitting\Nin a chair being tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are actually\Npotentially flying planes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,under these conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,3...2...1...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Clicking sound ]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Air whooshes ]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and pull\Nthat green lanyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam: So, our training is done\Nand we are ready to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent. Welcome.\NWelcome, everyone. [ Chuckles ]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, we went\Nthrough all of that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,just to be{\i1} passengers{\i}\Non the u-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we gotta do two things --\None, we gotta figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which one of us is gonna fly,\Nme or Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And two, we gotta let\Nthese professionals figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the logistics\Nof their flight plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: While Adam and Jamie\Nwait for flight clearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the guys decamp\Nto the perfect location
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for wind-protected\Nprecision flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam: We are testing the myth\Nthat multi-roters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,can possibly be lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is our multi-roter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our multi-roter pilot\NJames Franklin hyneman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is\Nour potential victim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with veins filled\Nwith blue blood --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,clearly a vulcan\Nwho we're going to steer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,this thing right into.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:22:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready to fly?\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Drone blades whirring ]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For this first test,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we're gonna get our little\Ncopter up about this high.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want this thing\Nflying at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a swarm\Nof angry bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then drive it right\Ninto the neck of our dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll see what happens\Nat that speed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with those propellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! [ Laughs ]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a perfect hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was going\Npretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Beep ]\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to me\Nthat anything at all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,happened to the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at the high speed\Nfootage of the multi-roter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,hitting the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the props bending\Nright out of the way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,even in the face of something\Nas soft as neck flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, clearly,\Nthey were designed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: Yep,\Nthe fly-it-out-of-the-box
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,quad-copter didn't make a dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But next up, the kid model.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's much scarier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: More likely to be\Nused for large deliveries,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it's heavier, has more power,\N6 roters,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and sturdier propellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.98,0:24:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what it can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oop. That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: Uh, take two?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.42,0:24:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going right for{\i1} me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.36,0:24:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.39,0:24:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughs ]\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.96,0:24:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not experiment\Non each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.03,0:24:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: The larger model\Nis proving trickier to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.04,0:24:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: But eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.24,0:24:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie gets it going\Nwhere he wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah,\Nyeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.24,0:24:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.71,0:24:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, bigger multi-roter,\Nbigger propellers,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.98,0:24:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,nice fat hit right here\Nin the vein, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.85,0:24:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No penetration.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.39,0:24:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.76,0:24:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,aside from being amazing pieces\Nof technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.59,0:24:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,these multi-roters are\Ngenuinely spooky to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.59,0:25:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One, they sound like\Na hive of angry bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.00,0:25:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Drone blades whirring ]\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.20,0:25:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, I am genuinely physically\Nafraid of them hitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.60,0:25:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently, that fear\Nis without any reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.44,0:25:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because we've been smacking them\Ninto our neck
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.51,0:25:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,without any injury whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.31,0:25:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So where does that leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.74,0:25:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.\NWe're the Mythbusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.01,0:25:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna sling\Nour camera platform into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.52,0:25:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This has 8 roters,\Nweighs 16 pounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.99,0:25:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and the propellers\Nare not made of plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.09,0:25:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that bends out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.59,0:25:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're made\Nof carbon fiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.49,0:25:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm genuinely scared about\Nwhat this is gonna do
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.73,0:25:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to this neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.63,0:25:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared and hopeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.54,0:25:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: The myth that one of\Nthese can cause a lethal injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.28,0:25:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is looking suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.08,0:25:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.21,0:25:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator:\NBut the team is dumping the two
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.02,0:25:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,realistic mid-range models...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.15,0:26:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And going for broke\Nwith the "Mythbusters" own
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.26,0:26:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,custom-made camera carrying\Nbehemoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.19,0:26:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Loudly ] I thought the other\Ntwo multi-roters were scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.99,0:26:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: Cue the team's\Nexpert pilot, Duncan,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.96,0:26:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and this myth's final chance\Nfor gory glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.37,0:26:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong.\NThat thing is terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.04,0:26:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie: This large multi-roter\Nis a different beast
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.47,0:26:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,than what we've been\Nhandling earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.78,0:26:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,\Nshall we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.95,0:26:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready?\NReady.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.68,0:26:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie: It's much bigger\Nand heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.98,0:26:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it starts to move\Ninto the neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.15,0:26:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't wanna just\Nbounce off
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.55,0:26:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I think this is gonna\Nactually do something
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.26,0:26:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to our neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.23,0:26:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.24,0:26:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.57,0:26:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughs ]\NLook at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.61,0:26:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.44,0:26:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad!\N[ Laughs ]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.54,0:26:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.51,0:27:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam: Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.65,0:27:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There you have it, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.85,0:27:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all fun and games\Nuntil someone loses an eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.09,0:27:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or a vein.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.46,0:27:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You put your finger there,\Nyou'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.20,0:27:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.97,0:27:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So what have we proven\Nafter all this mayhem?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.30,0:27:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we've actually proven\Ntwo different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.11,0:27:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On one hand,\Nthe smaller multi-roters
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.58,0:27:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you can buy at the store\Nare pretty darn safe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.28,0:27:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're designed\Nto be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.58,0:27:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a new hobby,\Nand there are lots of people
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.15,0:27:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,building larger\Nand larger multi-roters
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle bigger\Nand bigger payloads.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.45,0:27:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And when those multi-roters\Nget bigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.29,0:27:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the dangers they present\Nare absolutely real.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.16,0:27:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we've been looking\Nat a worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.16,0:27:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think we've gotta\Ncall this thing plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.26,0:27:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.00,0:27:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree, you know,\Nas a general rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.90,0:27:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I always try not to\Nput my neck
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.30,0:27:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,near large,\Nheavy, fast-moving objects
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.97,0:27:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with spinning blades on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.30,0:27:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's\Na good general rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.87,0:28:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here.\N[ Chuckles ]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.68,0:28:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥员: 4...3...\N稍微下降一点
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.55,0:28:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,回到beale
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.32,0:28:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,二人已经准备好对这则流言
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.96,0:28:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,进行最终测试
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.20,0:28:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们中只有一个人能上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.23,0:28:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,内个... [ sighs ] 你知道,\Nfor crying out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.80,0:28:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你对这种事情非常狂热
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.11,0:28:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你搜集这些东西\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.21,0:28:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，我大发慈悲地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.58,0:28:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不去否定你和你做这些事情的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.98,0:28:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很感激，谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.38,0:28:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,算你欠我一个人情\NOh, 我绝对欠你一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.99,0:28:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.32,0:28:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.12,0:28:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,绅士杰米下岗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.29,0:28:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,巨爽亚当上岗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.20,0:28:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我好兴奋啊！你看得出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.13,0:28:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,, ...For the defining,\Nnot quite hands-on test.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.67,0:29:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是时候\N去看看这架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.57,0:29:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟多难飞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.21,0:29:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会驾驶这架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是帮助评估
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.16,0:29:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是难以置信的一天\N在北加利福利亚这里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.76,0:29:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,天上几乎没有云
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.33,0:29:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,晴空万里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.70,0:29:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在今天飞行再好不过
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.86,0:30:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 亚当引擎启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.93,0:30:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.43,0:30:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当它达到一定转速
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.07,0:30:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我就会喷点油进去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.74,0:30:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙儿我们要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.71,0:30:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当现在肯定被吓尿了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.88,0:30:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 引擎咆哮 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.82,0:30:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的亚当,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.95,0:30:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你要确认一下增压操纵杆是否打到aft档
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.46,0:30:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还要确认在你左肋下的t-block有无打开的缺口
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.53,0:30:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没有打开的缺口
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.80,0:30:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,增压操纵杆也在aft档
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.17,0:30:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Radio chatter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.73,0:30:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我话你听，这架飞机飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.70,0:30:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,既独一无二又困难重重
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.04,0:30:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这需要一堆人在起飞前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.64,0:30:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,保障你的飞机一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.71,0:30:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，辅助轮人员已经拔出了辅助轮的插销
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.98,0:30:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因此当我们起飞时，辅助轮就会脱落了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.35,0:30:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Radio chatter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.52,0:30:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,检查单完成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.89,0:31:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离起飞仅剩数秒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.16,0:31:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Radio chatter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.19,0:31:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，我们起飞\N释放刹车，推满油门！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.20,0:31:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ 引擎咆哮 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.63,0:31:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿喂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.37,0:31:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.27,0:31:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哦天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.17,0:31:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这马力得多强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.10,0:31:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是，wow\N我们正在升空！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.28,0:31:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,碉堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.31,0:31:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.11,0:31:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.98,0:31:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,woc爬升得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.58,0:31:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!我们已经升空了，而且正向右滚转
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.66,0:31:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of a, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.02,0:31:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,take off that keeps the u-2\Nabove the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.33,0:31:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正不断爬升
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.37,0:31:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哇塞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.64,0:31:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.01,0:31:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughs ]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.35,0:32:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在爬升的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.76,0:32:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在作小半径转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.73,0:32:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在tricky的起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.43,0:32:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和疾速爬升后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.46,0:32:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天这太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.77,0:32:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,巴瑟缪罗上校和亚当
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.04,0:32:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,终于可以坐和放宽了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.20,0:32:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在超过珠穆朗玛峰的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.94,0:32:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,直到他们达到巡航高度
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.88,0:32:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在从以160节爬升的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.78,0:32:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,转入0.715马赫的巡航
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.45,0:32:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是音速的四分之三
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.92,0:32:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我到过的最高的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.29,0:32:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在接近60000英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.63,0:32:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,距地面12英里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.07,0:32:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,天空变成了非常非常暗的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.07,0:32:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是难以置信美的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.18,0:33:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,到了67500英尺这个高度
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.98,0:33:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Inhales deeply ]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.61,0:33:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就能看到我们地球的弧线了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.65,0:33:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这比我曾经见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.99,0:33:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,更加真实
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.66,0:33:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Inhales deeply,\Nexhales slowly ]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.53,0:33:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.76,0:33:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们绅士们，7w英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.43,0:33:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Inhales deeply,\Nexhales slowly ]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.90,0:33:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.47,0:33:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,除了空间站里的6名宇航员
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.44,0:33:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是地球上最高的两个人了（其实你更高一点）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.14,0:33:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,比普通商业航班
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.61,0:33:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行高度的两倍还高
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.42,0:33:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤，我有没提到我还穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.25,0:33:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一件增压宇航服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.26,0:33:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,被绑在一支火箭上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.16,0:33:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,以这样的方式度过一天还是蛮爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.43,0:33:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,杰米，我真的欠你一个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.17,0:34:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,复杂又繁琐的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.64,0:34:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,和费力的起飞\N似乎都烟消云散了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.61,0:34:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，看那
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.24,0:34:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. 那是旧金山\N那是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.05,0:34:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但这就是U-2的设计目的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.12,0:34:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在这待上几个小时，往下看
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.22,0:34:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,搜集情报
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.49,0:34:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果说商业航班上的景色很美
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.79,0:34:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这里的景色就是无与伦比的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.19,0:34:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrator: It's the maneuvers\Nat either end of proceedings
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.13,0:34:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,where the pilots earn\Nthe big bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.50,0:34:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,降落这架飞机的挑战是独一无二的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.80,0:34:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,而亚当即将要近距离体验
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.47,0:34:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,广告之后我们即将着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.64,0:34:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.08,0:34:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，太空男孩，你在上面还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.18,0:34:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好的不得了，杰米
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.75,0:34:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的景色无疑是惊人的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.76,0:34:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这种景象，我想到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.62,0:34:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,天空是幽暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.73,0:35:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你已经飞出了大气层的主体
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.43,0:35:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以俯瞰这层薄雾
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.70,0:35:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,环绕着
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.04,0:35:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的地球，让我们自由呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.14,0:35:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我能这么做，全靠成千上万人辛勤工作
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.61,0:35:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,得到的精巧设计
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.08,0:35:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将地里挖出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.78,0:35:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,变为奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.32,0:35:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机如此，增压服亦如此
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.09,0:35:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Inhales deeply,\Nexhales slowly ]
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.06,0:35:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,荣幸至极
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.20,0:35:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man.\NThat is a lot of horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.17,0:35:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, we're already lifting.\NThat's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.31,0:35:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.08,0:35:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God,\Nthe view is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.06,0:36:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.56,0:36:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,毋庸置疑，U-2这款高空侦察机
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.30,0:36:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是航空技术的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.97,0:36:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,机长需要苹果派
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.47,0:36:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.54,0:36:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.47,0:36:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好餈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.41,0:36:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最难飞的飞机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.11,0:36:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人开着这种飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.28,0:36:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,每次超过12到14小时，Mmm好餈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.98,0:36:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,恩，而在这艰巨的飞行之后
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.22,0:36:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have some butt\Nshimmying exercises
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.56,0:36:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来防止你发麻
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.76,0:36:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它称作\N构建屁股的愈伤组织
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.16,0:36:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Adam laughs ]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.60,0:36:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,该降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.97,0:36:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，准备下高
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.04,0:36:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是橡胶遇见跑道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.54,0:36:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,准备打开起落架
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.71,0:36:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你可能会听到一些闷响
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.11,0:36:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能是对所有飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.54,0:36:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最大的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.28,0:37:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,两起落架落下并锁住
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.22,0:37:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始收油门
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.55,0:37:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,蛟龙夫人着陆时后轮先触地
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.15,0:37:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上这时记忆已经失速
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.82,0:37:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这就像降落一辆自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.69,0:37:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只有机身中间的两组起落架
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.33,0:37:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行员已经放下了起落架
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.27,0:37:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,并且通过一些措施增加了阻力
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.13,0:37:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以当我们到达跑道时，她就足够慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.84,0:37:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就可以着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.91,0:37:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但这还没完，还有地面效应
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.88,0:37:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,U-2的大展弦比机翼和与之相称的高升力
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.48,0:37:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,意味着在最终进近时，她会发飘
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.42,0:37:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,需要不可思议的技巧来控制
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.39,0:37:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还有视野问题
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.09,0:37:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是追逐车
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.89,0:37:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,由真正的U-2飞行员驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.73,0:37:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为飞机里的飞行员只有有限的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.93,0:37:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至看不见跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.97,0:37:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当他接近跑道时
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.57,0:37:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,车里的飞行员就会一英尺一英尺引导他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.21,0:38:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,让他在正确的时间，正确的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.21,0:38:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,作出正确的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.51,0:38:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正处于临界速度
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.65,0:38:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,高度2300，航向207
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.75,0:38:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在到了有趣的部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.65,0:38:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这部分让我赚到U-2飞行员奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.53,0:38:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，有个家伙在我们前面进入了跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.30,0:38:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Car engine revs ]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.34,0:38:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yee-haw.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.27,0:38:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,起落架放下，襟翼全开，减速板打开
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.47,0:38:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,灯光打开
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.48,0:38:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,扰流板预位
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.78,0:38:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,设定完毕，准备着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.39,0:38:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Radio chatter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.29,0:38:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看那
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥员：15...12...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.89,0:38:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,10...8...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.39,0:38:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,7...6...5...4...3...稍微压下杆...4.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.70,0:39:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,3, 2, 稳住，1英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.30,0:39:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... [ chuckles ]\N[ Chuckles ]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.04,0:39:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Beeping ]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.38,0:39:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Monitor beeping rapidly ]\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.91,0:39:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥员：漂亮，欢迎回来，绅士们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.48,0:39:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,根据传统，不管落得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.85,0:39:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他都得说很漂亮\NOh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.62,0:39:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这段旅程非常愉快，谢谢你，亚当
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.86,0:39:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们古老的欢迎委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.49,0:39:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，关车
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.86,0:39:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，编辑们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.93,0:39:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能给我们在流言终结者里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.93,0:39:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,做过的惊人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.83,0:39:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,来个蒙太奇
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.20,0:39:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.70,0:39:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想，在沙漠里飞一辆火箭车
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.94,0:39:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看着火箭滑橇超过音速
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.14,0:39:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然后撞上一堵不动墙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.15,0:39:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Explosion ]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.45,0:39:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我巨爽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.05,0:39:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,滑下200英尺的水梯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.12,0:39:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,飞上70英尺的空中，然后落入一个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.79,0:39:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, yeah!\NMan: He was like, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.06,0:39:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]\NCheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.36,0:40:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为两个原因，这次的体验冠绝于他们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.86,0:40:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.24,0:40:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,难以重复
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.07,0:40:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.04,0:40:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of superlatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.61,0:40:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚被绑在火箭上两个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.21,0:40:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着一件太空服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.31,0:40:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,飞到了大气层的边界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.62,0:40:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个有利位置看我的家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.15,0:40:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个看桥的好位置
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.62,0:40:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不可思议的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.76,0:40:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,完全独一无二
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.83,0:40:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，亚当，你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.86,0:40:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为，我的意思是，这被期望为
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.17,0:40:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,最难飞的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.80,0:40:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们还没见过其他飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.10,0:40:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，但我们见识了这架
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一架专为特殊任务设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.91,0:40:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,特殊机体
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.11,0:40:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,它比其他飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.35,0:40:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,更多的机组人员
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.41,0:40:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,和更繁琐的协议
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.12,0:40:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而这也是唯一要求飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.62,0:40:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,除了宇航员
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.55,0:41:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,穿宇航服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.66,0:41:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a bad way\Nto spend your day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.06,0:41:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为应该把它归入有此可能
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.23,0:41:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.90,0:41:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还应该把它归入“狂拽炫酷屌炸天”的一类
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.80,0:41:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然，我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.31,0:41:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当，你知道她为啥被称为蛟龙夫人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.31,0:41:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.84,0:41:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你不知道她降落起来像只蛟龙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.48,0:41:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还是像个夫人
